        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "Morgan Stanley Bank, N.A. (\"MSBNA\") and Morgan Stanley Private Bank, National Association (\"MSPBNA\") are our U.S. Bank Subsidiaries, (together, \"U.S. Bank Subsidiaries\").",
